# /raw is a local-only drop zone for unstructured source material that gets
# synthesized into MDX content. Everything in here is gitignored except this
# .gitignore and the README that documents the convention.
#
# To preserve a specific raw artifact in git (e.g. an architecture sketch worth
# keeping forever), add a `!path/to/file` exception below.

*
!.gitignore
!README.md
